sentence: how many rivers do not traverse the state with the capital albany ?
sentence-with-vars: how many rivers do not traverse the state with the capital city0 ?
sql: select count ( river.river_name ) from river where river.traverse not in ( select state.state_name from state where state.capital = ' albany ' ) ;
sql-with-vars: select count ( river.river_name ) from river where river.traverse not in ( select state.state_name from state where state.capital = ' city0 ' ) ;
